bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":12,"text":"and Booz begot Obed, and Obed begot Jessæ.","searchKeywords":["and","booz","begot","obed","jess"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_13","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":13,"text":"And Jessæ begot his first-born Eliab, Aminadab the second, Samaa the third,","searchKeywords":["and","jess","begot","his","first","born","eliab","aminadab","the","second","samaa","third"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_14","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":14,"text":"Nathanael the fourth, Zabdai the fifth,","searchKeywords":["nathanael","the","fourth","zabdai","fifth"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_15","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":15,"text":"Asam the sixth, David the seventh.","searchKeywords":["asam","the","sixth","david","seventh"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_16","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":16,"text":"And their sister Saruia, and Abigaia: and the sons of Saruia Abisa, and Joab, and Asael, three.","searchKeywords":["and","their","sister","saruia","abigaia","the","sons","abisa","joab","asael","three"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_17","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":17,"text":"And Abigaia bore Amessab: and the father of Amessab Jothor the Ismaelite.","searchKeywords":["and","abigaia","bore","amessab","the","father","jothor","ismaelite"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_18","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":18,"text":"And Chaleb the son of Esrom took Gazuba to wife, and Jerioth: and these her sons; Jasar, and Subab, and Ardon.","searchKeywords":["and","chaleb","the","son","esrom","took","gazuba","wife","jerioth","these","her","sons","jasar","subab","ardon"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_19","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":19,"text":"And Gazuba died; and Chaleb took to himself Ephrath, and she bore to him Or.","searchKeywords":["and","gazuba","died","chaleb","took","himself","ephrath","she","bore","him"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_20","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":20,"text":"And Or begot Uri, and Uri begot Beseleel.","searchKeywords":["and","begot","uri","beseleel"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_21","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":21,"text":"And after this Esron went in to the daughter of Machir the father of Galaad, and he took her when he was sixty-five years old; and she bore him Seruch.","searchKeywords":["and","after","this","esron","went","the","daughter","machir","father","galaad","took","her","when","was","sixty","five","years","old","she","bore","him","seruch"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_22","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":22,"text":"And Seruch begot Jair, and he had twenty-three cities in Galaad.","searchKeywords":["and","seruch","begot","jair","had","twenty","three","cities","galaad"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_23","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":23,"text":"And he took Gedsur and Aram, the towns of Jair from them; Canath and its towns, sixty cities. All these the sons of Machir the father of Galaad.","searchKeywords":["and","took","gedsur","aram","the","towns","jair","from","them","canath","its","sixty","cities","all","these","sons","machir","father","galaad"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_24","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":24,"text":"And after the death of Esron, Chaleb came to Ephratha; and the wife of Esron Abia; and she bore him Ascho the father of Thecoe.","searchKeywords":["and","after","the","death","esron","chaleb","came","ephratha","wife","abia","she","bore","him","ascho","father","thecoe"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_25","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":25,"text":"And the sons of Jerameel the first-born of Esron , the first-born Ram, and Banaa, and Aram, and Asan his brother.","searchKeywords":["and","the","sons","jerameel","first","born","esron","ram","banaa","aram","asan","his","brother"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_26","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":26,"text":"And Jerameel had another wife, and her name Atara: she is the mother of Ozom.","searchKeywords":["and","jerameel","had","another","wife","her","name","atara","she","the","mother","ozom"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_27","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":27,"text":"And the sons of Ram the first-born of Jerameel were Maas, and Jamin, and Acor.","searchKeywords":["and","the","sons","ram","first","born","jerameel","were","maas","jamin","acor"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_28","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":28,"text":"And the sons of Ozom were, Samai, and Jadae: and the sons of Samai; Nadab, and Abisur.","searchKeywords":["and","the","sons","ozom","were","samai","jadae","nadab","abisur"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_29","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":29,"text":"And the name of the wife of Abisur Abichaia, and she bore him Achabar, and Moel.","searchKeywords":["and","the","name","wife","abisur","abichaia","she","bore","him","achabar","moel"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_30","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":30,"text":"And the sons of Nadab; Salad and Apphain; and Salad died without children.","searchKeywords":["and","the","sons","nadab","salad","apphain","died","without","children"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_31","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":31,"text":"And the sons of Apphain, Isemiel; and the sons of Isemiel, Sosan; and the sons of Sosan, Dadai.","searchKeywords":["and","the","sons","apphain","isemiel","sosan","dadai"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_32","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":32,"text":"And the sons of Dadai, Achisamas, Jether, Jonathan: and Jether died childless.","searchKeywords":["and","the","sons","dadai","achisamas","jether","jonathan","died","childless"]},{"verseId":"brenton_1-chronicles_2_33","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":13,"bookName":"1 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"1-chronicles","chapter":2,"verse":33,"text":"And the sons of Jonathan; Phaleth, and Hozam. These were the sons of Jerameel.","searchKeywords":["and","the","sons","jonathan","phaleth","hozam","these","were